&lt;unk&gt; pooja &lt;unk&gt; is a 1975 indian kannada film , directed by h. v. rajendra singh and produced by s v rajan singh . the film stars srinath , b. v. radha , b. v. radha and b. v. radha singh . the film stars srinath , b. v. radha , b. v. radha and b. v. radha in lead roles . the film had musical score by chellapilla satyam .